## Naming Conventions

```
Components:   PascalCase     → ToolCard.tsx, FeatureEditor.tsx
API routes:   kebab-case     → analyze-drawing/, site-plan-generator/
DB tables:    snake_case     → permit_projects, permit_documents
Types:        PascalCase     → RenderingInterpretation, SitePlanInputs
Functions:    camelCase      → generateSitePlanSvg(), analyzeDrawing()
Constants:    SCREAMING_SNAKE → RENDERING_INTERPRETER_PROMPT
```

---

## What Not to Build

- No automated ePlan / LADBS portal submission
- No final stamped document generation — all output is engineer-reviewed draft
- No image or file storage in DB — store file path references only
- No AI in Tool 3 (Lot Calculator) — pure math only
- No AI in SVG/DXF generation (Tool 7) — pure functions only
- No feature that bypasses the engineer confirmation gate
- No non-pool project types in Tool 7 yet